{
    "description_long": "This is a sleek, black sports car with a low, aerodynamic profile and a pronounced rear spoiler, designed for high performance and speed. The body features smooth, flowing lines and a compact two-door coupe shape, with a sharply sloped roof and wide stance. The front end is aggressive, with angular headlights and a wide grille, while the rear showcases distinctive taillights and a prominent spoiler for added downforce. The car sits on large, five-spoke alloy wheels with low-profile tires, emphasizing its sporty character. The windows are tinted, and the side mirrors are streamlined to reduce drag. The overall appearance suggests a modern, high-end sports car suitable for urban streets or racetracks.",
